Once you have achieved your goal, write "> done" to end the game.

message.content: The "drop" action lets you remove an item from your inventory, placing it in your current room. For example, if you type "> drop book," the book will leave your inventory and appear on the floor where you are.

clem_player.response: The "drop" action lets you remove an item from your inventory, placing it in your current room. For example, if you type "> drop book," the book will leave your inventory and appear on the floor where you are.
